(4497, 337, 'bold_text', 'SkipTraze is an international skip tracing platform, connecting debt collectors with fresh contact information of debtors. We do this by connecting debt collection agencies to a wide range of sales databases (SkipTraze Data Partners) in a compliant way.'),
(4498, 337, 'platform_text', 'Our service is novel and game changer - no longer are debt collectors restricted by the data they have and/or contracting expensive private investigators and/or accessing old databases from governments or other players. Now debt collection departments can chose the freshness of data they want to receive - shared by the consumer directly and with consent.\r\n\r\nWe have developed an easy-to-use solution for skip tracing, to make debt collection department lives easier and widen their options to contact debtors significantly.'),
(4499, 337, 'team_heading', 'Meet our team'),
(4500, 337, 'team_list_0_image', '227'),
(4501, 337, 'team_list_0_name', 'Aleksandra Van Dulst'),
(4502, 337, 'team_list_0_designation', 'CEO and Board Member'),
(4503, 337, 'team_list_0_description', 'Aleksandra founded SkipTraze in 2022. A former Regional bank CEO, Aleksandra led Novum Bank Group\'s expansion to Poland.\r\nAleksandra has led and scaled a bank branch for Novum Bank and a non-bank lender in Poland. Additionally she founded Fininova - a Fintech management advisory firm.'),
(4504, 337, 'team_list_0_link', ''),
(4505, 337, 'team_list_1_image', '227'),
(4506, 337, 'team_list_1_name', 'Dawid Pruchniewski'),
(4507, 337, 'team_list_1_designation', 'Board Member'),
(4508, 337, 'team_list_1_description', 'Dawid founded SkipTraze after seeing non-contactable portfolio problems in collection industry. A former Senior Specialist at the biggest credit reference agency in Poland - BIK.\r\nDawid is a serial entrepreneur and has founded RiskBite - an AI analytics company delivering risk decision models to financial institutions in Poland.'),
(4509, 337, 'team_list_1_link', ''),
(4510, 337, 'team_list_2_image', '227'),
(4511, 337, 'team_list_2_name', 'Hans Tamm'),
(4512, 337, 'team_list_2_designation', 'Board Member'),
(4513, 337, 'team_list_2_description', 'Hans as a Board Member is overseeing international data partnerships and business development. Hans is an experienced business development executive.\r\nHans has scaled several businesses internationally, including Fiizy and Click & Grow. He currently serves as a Board Member of an international affiliate network and lead generation business DoAff.'),
(4514, 337, 'team_list_2_link', ''),
(4515, 337, 'team_list_3_image', '227'),
(4516, 337, 'team_list_3_name', 'Artis Gromuls'),
(4517, 337, 'team_list_3_designation', 'Board Member'),
(4518, 337, 'team_list_3_description', 'Artis as a Board Member is overseeing collection department partnerships. Artis is a serial entrepreneur and experienced Board Member.\r\nArtis has previously worked as a leader at Nokia and has founded several software and FinTech startups. He currently serves as a Board Member of an international affiliate network and lead generation business DoAff.'),
