(4842, 340, '_team_list_0_designation', 'field_651f7ca908344'),
(4843, 340, 'team_list_0_description', 'Aleksandra founded SkipTraze in 2022. A former Regional bank CEO, Aleksandra led Novum Bank Group\'s expansion to Poland.\r\nAleksandra has led and scaled a bank branch for Novum Bank and a non-bank lender in Poland. Additionally she founded Fininova - a Fintech management advisory firm.'),
