(5732, 387, 'team_list_1_description', 'Dawid founded SkipTraze after seeing non-contactable portfolio problems in collection industry. A former Senior Specialist at the biggest credit reference agency in Poland - BIK.\r\nDawid is a serial entrepreneur and has founded RiskBite - an AI analytics company delivering risk decision models to financial institutions in Poland.'),
