(7368, 449, 'content_title', 'No contact, no willingness to pay? Wrong!'),
(7369, 449, '_content_title', 'field_651d15af49a06'),
(7370, 449, 'content_subtext', 'When buying non-performing loan (NPL) portfolios one of the biggest problems is the fact that contact information about the debtor is outdated. Their email, phone number and address is no longer actual. This means even if the debtor has the ability to pay, there is no wildness due to no communication.'),
