(7797, 464, '_about_us_image', 'field_651f6dbbfd601'),
(7798, 464, 'bold_text', 'SkipTraze is an international skip tracing platform, connecting debt collectors with fresh contact information of debtors. We do this by connecting debt collection agencies to a wide range of sales databases (SkipTraze Data Partners) in a compliant way.'),
(7799, 464, '_bold_text', 'field_651f71aae0e90'),
(7800, 464, 'platform_text', 'Our service is novel and game changer - no longer are debt collectors restricted by the data they have and/or contracting expensive private investigators and/or accessing old databases from governments or other players. Now debt collection departments can chose the freshness of data they want to receive - shared by the consumer directly and with consent.\r\n\r\nWe have developed an easy-to-use solution for skip tracing, to make debt collection department lives easier and widen their options to contact debtors significantly.'),
